<font face="arial"><b>Computer Department Return Policy</b></font>
<br>
<ul>
<li>Returns must be accompanied by the original receipt or invoice.
<li>Products must be returned within two weeks (14 days) of purchase in unopened, original package and be in salable condition.
<li>There are no returns on opened product without prior managerial approval. Please confirm compatibility prior to purchase.
<li>A 15% restocking fee will be charged for returned products.
<li>Defective merchandise will either be replaced or repaired per the manufacturer's warranty.
</ul>
<p>

<font face="arial"><b>Check Cashing Policy</b></font>
<br>
The University of Idaho Bookstore will accept your personal check in payment for merchandise under the following conditions:
<ul>
<li>It is your personal check or that of your parents.
<li>The check is not made out for more than three dollars ($3.00) over the amount of purchase.
<li>You must present picture identification, either student ID or current driver's license.
</ul>
<p>

<font face="arial"><b>Buy Back - Cash for your Books</b></font>
<br>
The University of Idaho Bookstore will buy back books provided they are your own books and they are being used the following semester.  A major wholesaler will purchase most textbooks during the buy back period (finals week).  To sell your books you do not need your sales receipt.
<p>
<a href="./books/buyback.asp">More detailed information on Buy Back</a> is available.

